name: Into The Badlands 02
description:
Toadstool Geologic Park is a key link in understanding the earth’s history from 38 to 24 million years ago. Geologists consider it the “type section for the White River Group,” meaning that all other similar aged deposits in North America are compared to the geologic standard designated at Toadstool. 

Toadstool Geologic Park, Nebraska
